&lt;p&gt;The suitable candidate will have&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional customer service skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An understanding of IT systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be able to work efficiently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be able to demonstrate flexibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working hours will be across multiple sites between the hours of 8am to 6pm Monday to Friday and include Saturday/Sunday mornings and late nights on a rota basis.&lt;/p&gt;
